      "\"Well hello there, this is TV on the radio, Thomas Vance, the music vendor, welcome to the Friday Rock Show, mate! Right, we have the usual tight, tough and heavy selection of your kind of stuff hitting the airwaves between now and midnight. We have a festering stack of thunder and thump to get your ears attuned, alright?\"",
